==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Goddess
<hw>God"dess</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>A female
god; a divinity, or deity, of the female sex.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>When the daughter of Jupiter presented herself among a crowd of
<qex>goddesses</qex>, she was distinguished by her graceful stature and
superior beauty.</q> <rj><qau>Addison.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A woman of superior charms or excellence.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Gode</ent>⟦br⟧
